        <abstract>
            <p>CD has written to Asa Gray criticising J. D. Dana’s arguments for a warm period subsequent to glacial period.</p>
            <p>Remembers it is Alphonse de Candolle who states that many species are not true species.</p> 
<p>Did Huxley write the excellent review in the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi>?</p> 
        </abstract>
